name: Sätra Brunn DAO
description: Sätra Brunn is a 144 acre wellness destination in the suburbs of Stockholm, Sweden, renowned for its healing spring water and picturesque scenery. Sätra Brunn DAO plans to buy Sätra Brunn at auction to establish the first-ever real world DAO-governed municipality.
payDisclosure: Contributions made to Sätra Brunn DAO are donations, and should not be made in anticipation of financial gain.
